类 PowerSDK

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    ConnectListenerSubject, MountDeviceListenerSubject

    public class PowerSDK
extends BasePowerSDK
    包含挂载和连接的所有方法以及回调 Contains all the methods and the callbacks of mount and link. 
     
    
 1，初始化SDK连接     Initialize the connection of SDK.
 执行startConnectSDK startConnectSDK(com.powervision.powersdk.factory.base.BaseConnectIpAndPort)方法    execute startConnectSDK startConnectSDK(com.powervision.powersdk.factory.base.BaseConnectIpAndPort) method.
 
    
 2，注册SDK连接回调，否则ConnectListener或者ConnectListener.SimpleConnectListener(一个简化的ConnectListener)    Register the callback of SDK connection,otherwise,ConnectListener or ConnectListener.SimpleConnectListener (A simplified ConnectListener)
 不需要实现全部回调方法, 后面两个回调简称为ConnectListener)的回调方法不会执行     don't need to implement all of the callback methods.callback methods called ConnectListener) would not be executed.
 执行startRegisterConnectCallbackstartRegisterConnectCallback()方法  execute startRegisterConnectCallbackstartRegisterConnectCallback() method.
 
    
 3，通过BasePowerSDK.addConnectListener(ConnectListener)注册ConnectListener Register ConnectListener by BasePowerSDK.addConnectListener(ConnectListener).
 
    
 4，进行链路连接操作，回调在ConnectListener.onChainConnected()中返回  Connect link and callback in ConnectListener.onChainConnected().
 执行connectChain JNINativeManager.connectChain()方法   execute connectChain JNINativeManager.connectChain() method.
 
    
 5，在ConnectListener.onChainConnected()中进行设备连接操作,回调在ConnectListener.onDroneConnected()中返回Connect device in ConnectListener.onChainConnected() and callback in ConnectListener.onDroneConnected().
 执行connectDevice JNINativeManager.connectDevice()方法  execute connectDevice JNINativeManager.connectDevice() method.
 
    
 6，在ConnectListener.onDroneConnected()中注册挂载的回调，相关的其他挂载回调通过PowerSDK的addXXXListener方法实现 Register the callback of mount in ConnectListener.onDroneConnected().relevant mount callbacks can realized by addXXXListener of PowerSDK.
 执行startRegisterMountCallback startRegisterMountCallback()方法         execute startRegisterMountCallback startRegisterMountCallback() method.
 
    
 7，断开的SDK的操作步骤                                     operation steps about disconnecting the SDK.
 1）断开设备连接在ConnectListener.onDeviceDisconnected()回调   Disconnect device and callback in ConnectListener.onDeviceDisconnected().
 执行disconnectDevice JNINativeManager.disconnectDevice()方法      execute disconnectDevice JNINativeManager.disconnectDevice() method.
 2) 断开链路连接ConnectListener.onChainDisconnected()回调 Disconnect link and callback in ConnectListener.onChainDisconnected().
 执行disconnectChain JNINativeManager.disconnectChain()方法        execute disconnectChain JNINativeManager.disconnectChain() method.
 3）断开SDK连接，执行JNINativeManager.unInitSDK()方法           Disconnect the SDK and execute JNINativeManager.unInitSDK() method.

        public void setUartParam(int bps,
                         int dataBits,
                         int stopBits,
                         int parity,

        设置Uart参数接口 Set the interface parameters of Uart.

        在MountDeviceListener.UartListener#onUartParamSet(int, int)中返回 Return at MountDeviceListener.UartListener#onUartParamSet(int, int)method.

        参数:
        bps - 串口波特率 0:9600 1:14400 2:19200 3:38400 4:57600 5:115200 串口波特率 0:9600 1:14400 2:19200 3:38400 4:57600 5:115200 Baudrate 0: 9600 1:14400 2:19200 3:38400 4:57600 5:115200
        dataBits - 数据位数 0:8位 1:9位 Data bits 0:8bits 1:9bits
        stopBits - 停止位数 0:1位 1:2位 Stop bits 0:1bits 1:2bits
        parity - 校验 0:无校验 1:奇校验 2:偶校验 Verify 0:No verification 1: odd parity check2:even parity check
        flowCtrl - 流控 0:无流控 1:RTS有效 2:CTS有效 3:RTS和CTS同时有效 Fluid control0:No fluid control 1:RTS is effective 2:CTS is effective 3:RTS和CTS are effective at the same time.

      • setGpioParam

        public void setGpioParam(int deviceNumber,
                         int periodRatio,
                         int periodLow,
                         int periodTotal)
        设置GPIO参数接口 Set the interface parameters of GPIO.

        结果在MountDeviceListener.GpioListener#onGpioParamSet(int, int)中返回 Return at MountDeviceListener.GpioListener#onGpioParamSet(int, int) method.

        参数:
        deviceNumber - gpio设备编号 0:gpio1 1:gpio2 2:gpio3 gpio Device number 0:gpio1 1:gpio2 2:gpio3
        periodRatio - 周期值分辨率,取值范围(0~0xffff),单位 1/64us（需要大于0）The span of period resolution is (0~0xffff).Units 1/64us(Be greater than 0).
        periodLow - 一个周期内低电平持续时间, 取值范围(0~0xffffffff), 值为0表示输出固定高电平 分辨率50us The span of low level duration in one cycle is (0~0xffffffff).The value of 0 means output high level.resolution 50us.
        periodTotal - 周期持续总时间,取值范围(0~0xffffffff), 值为 0 表示输出固定低电平,分辨率 50us The span of cycle total duration is (0~0xffffffff).The value of 0 means output low level.resolution 50us.
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - periodTotal需大于periodLow IllegalArgumentException periodTotal must be greater than periodLow.
        另请参阅:
        MountApiGpioParam
